asset.author: Braun
asset.hookText:
People normally associate hiphop with the street, clubs and DIY studios, mics and mixtapes. But barbershop have always been a meeting point for hiphop culture. Shaveyourstyle.com asked one of Spain's most respected rap and hiphop artists, Mucho Muchacho, why he wanted to create a New York style barbershop in Barcelona.

www.shaveyourstyle.com
www.creambarbershop.blogspot.com

Music: MUCHO MUCHACHO - Será Mejor (Cookin' Soul REMIX)
